    "text": "This key displays a message indicating a subscription has been deactivated due to non-payment. It appears within the Portal Settings, specifically in the Payments section for SaaS services, likely to inform the user about the reason for their service interruption. Translators should ensure the message accurately conveys the reason for deactivation and its impact.",
